---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-brand-dark text-brand-sage-light/75 pt-20 pb-10 border-t border-brand-sage/10 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle backdrops -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-sage clip-leaf-right blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8 pb-16 border-b border-brand-sage-dark/30">
      
      <!-- Column 1: Brand Info (col-span-4) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6">
        <a href="#inicio" class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
          <span class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-white group-hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">AURA</span>
          <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-champagne"></div>
        </a>
        <p class="font-sans text-xs md:text-sm text-brand-sage-light/60 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Medicina estética premium enfocada en resaltar tu belleza natural con seguridad médica y la máxima sutilidad. Viví la experiencia de un cuidado diseñado para tu armonía individual.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Social Icons -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <!-- Instagram -->
          <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-sage-dark/55 hover:bg-brand-sage text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-colors duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transform shadow-md" aria-label="Instagram">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.051.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 1 0 0 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 0 0 0-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 1 1 0-8 4 4 0 0 1 0 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 1 0 0 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 0 0 0-2.881z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <!-- Facebook -->
          <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-brand-sage-dark/55 hover:bg-brand-sage text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-colors duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transform shadow-md" aria-label="Facebook">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 2: Navigation Links (col-span-3) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-6 lg:pl-10">
        <h3 class="font-display text-sm tracking-widest uppercase font-semibold text-white">Navegación</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 font-sans text-xs md:text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="#inicio" class="hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">Inicio</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#sobre-nosotros" class="hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">Sobre Nosotros</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#servicios" class="hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">Servicios</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#opiniones" class="hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">Opiniones</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#contacto" class="hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">Contacto</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Column 3: Legal & Regulatory Info (col-span-5) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-6">
        <h3 class="font-display text-sm tracking-widest uppercase font-semibold text-white">Cumplimiento Legal</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-sage-light/50 font-light leading-relaxed">
          Nuestra clínica opera bajo las más estrictas normativas nacionales de salud. Todos los tratamientos son realizados por médicos matriculados activos que utilizan insumos autorizados por ANMAT.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-2 font-sans text-xs text-brand-sage-light/60">
          <p>• Habilitación del Ministerio de Salud: Reg. Nº 1845/26</p>
          <p>• Dirección Médica: Dra. Valentina Bianco (M.N. 123.456)</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom copyright / Legal links -->
    <div class="pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-between items-center font-sans text-xs text-brand-sage-light/45">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} Aura Medicina Estética. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      
      <!-- Privacy, terms, and cancellation link structures -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 justify-center">
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">Política de Privacidad</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">Términos de Servicio</a>
        <a href="/cancellation" class="hover:text-brand-champagne transition-colors duration-300">Política de Cancelación</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
